Project Overview

Create a user-friendly, simple accounting desktop application designed specifically for small businesses. It will be developed using nextjs frontend and MySQL as the backend database to ensure reliable data storage.

Tech Stack

Frontend: Electron NextJs 14 (Typescript, tailwindcss 4)

Will be building the app both as electron and nextjs app for web browser.

Backend Database: MySQL

ORM (Optional but recommended): Sequelize (Node.js ORM)

